  validate_presence_of(${1:column})

snippet validate_uniqueness_of
abbr    validate_uniqueness_of(...)
alias   uniq
regexp  '\v((to|should|to_not|should_not)\s|\.$)'
options word
  validate_uniqueness_of(${1:column})${2:.scoped_to: ${3:scope_name\}}${4:.case_insensitive}
